&lt;li&gt;Balanced: Adapt methods to business questions and data realities, acknowledging limitations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Rigorous: Maintain methodological integrity and quantify the sensitivity of findings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Innovative: Invest in advancing measurement science and developing new methods.&lt;/li&gt;
