&lt;p&gt;The Segmentation Platform is in the middle of a major evolution — building a near real-time customer segmentation architecture, on-the-fly targeting, new entity types, and deeper data infrastructure integrations. The Insights Platform is extending into AI/ML-driven anomaly detection and trend analysis. Critically, both platforms are beginning to incorporate autonomous agent pipelines that handle complex, multi-step workflows at scale — and you will be the leader who ensures these systems are built with the rigor, reliability, and operational maturity that production-grade agentic systems demand.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your leadership will directly determine how well these platforms scale to meet Airbnb&#39;s ambitions, how confidently partner teams can depend on them, and how effectively this team leads Airbnb&#39;s broader shift toward AI-native engineering.&lt;/p&gt;
