&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10+ years of B2C CRM/lifecycle experience in fast-paced consumer or e-commerce environments with a track record of high-impact work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of lifecycle marketing, custom

